GitHub Action "Auto Assign"

The Action

Action consists of
- some information about the action. like name and description
- inputs
    parameters handed over from a corresponding workflow
- runs
    one or more steps processed one after another
    each step can
    - call another action
    - include a shell like script
    - hand over informations to the next step

The Workflow

Workflow consists of
- name of the workflow
- events that triggers the action
    such as labeling or unlabeling a pull request
- some initial actions
- all "inputs" information for the action
